SLO:
---
- It is a principled way of saying what level of downtime is acceptable.
- Error rate: Acceptable error rate
- Latency expectations

Observable system gives you: context, status, expectations, debuggability

How good your intrumentaiton tol must be:
- Must have integration for Web, RPC and storage client
- Context aware(canary or prod)
- Support all languages
- Support many analysis tools
- Developers need to add custom instrumentation

 Look in to this opencensus.io for GRPC
